insert(DLL.Data storage,uint256,uint256,.details: Inserts a new node between _prev and _next. When inserting a node already existing in  the list it will be automatically removed from the old position.

params._curr: the id of the new node being inserted
params._next: the node which _new will be inserted before
params._prev: the node which _new will be inserted after
